      <t>  The GSMP charter calls for a draft to propose how to
  encapsulate GSMP messages in IP packet &lt;draft-doria-gsmp-
  applicability-00.txt&gt;. This memo recommends using TCP as
  the transport to carry GSMP message over IP.

